[Scala project template using sbt]

Default dependencies:
- H2 (http://www.h2database.com) - Java database
- Squeryl (http://squeryl.org) - ORM
- ScalaTest (http://www.scalatest.org/) - Testing
- Borachio (http://borachio.com/) - Mocking

Plugins:
- sbteclipse (https://github.com/typesafehub/sbteclipse) - Eclipse project generator

Usage:
1. clone the repository
  `git clone git@github.com:ACN-AST/scala-template.git`

2. edit `build.sbt` and change the default name
  name := "scala-template"

3. put your scala sources under "src/main/scala"

4. generate the eclipse project: `sbt eclipse`